section.hiking-trail
    .container
        .hiking-trail__wrapper
            .hiking-trail-title
                h3.main-title We envision a world  where everyone has permanent access to a hiking trail
            .hiking-trail__card-column
                .hiking-trail__card-item
                    .hiking-trail__card
                        h4.hiking-trail__card-title Advocate
                        p.hiking-trail__card-text We work with Congress, Federal agencies, and partners on policy issues and legislation to ensure funding for trails, preservation of natural areas, and protection of the hiking experience.
                        .hiking-trail__card-img
                            img(src="./img/main/vector-3.png", alt="")
                .hiking-trail__card-item
                    .hiking-trail__card
                        h4.hiking-trail__card-title Volunteer
                        p.hiking-trail__card-text Trails don't maintain themselves. Individuals of any age and experience level can become trail stewards. Give back to the trails you love, meet new people, and enjoy the experience!
                        .hiking-trail__card-img
                            img(src="./img/main/vector-2.png", alt="")
                .hiking-trail__card-item
                    .hiking-trail__card
                        h4.hiking-trail__card-title Explore
                        p.hiking-trail__card-text Feel confident when you set out on your next trail adventure. Check out our free hiking resources like tips for hiking with families, gear checklists, finding the best trail for you.
                        .hiking-trail__card-img
                            img(src="./img/main/vector-1.png", alt="")
                    a(href="#").hiking-trail__card-button.header__button Learn More





 



